title: MisterMusic Show 344 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 344    [120 minutes]  192kbps MP3 -



New music on this week's show from Black Rivers who are the Williams brothers of the alternative rock band Doves. Also new stuff from Absofacto, and another new track from the latest album by Gang of Four.

We go back in time 42 years to 1973 for the 'Oldie of the Week'. The song spent 3 weeks at number 1 in the US and 4 weeks in Canada that year.
(Practice your 'na-na-na-na-na 's to sing along).

Plus the usual mix of over 5 decades of indie, alternative and rock hits.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
